https://github.com/FiloSottile/mkcert

> on macOS
```bash
brew install mkcert
mkcert -install
```

```bash
mkcert \
-cert-file mcp.sea-flea.local.crt \
-key-file mcp.sea-flea.local.key \
sea-flea.local "*.sea-flea.local" localhost 127.0.0.1 ::1
```

Then add the following line to your `/etc/hosts` file:

```bash
0.0.0.0 mcp.sea-flea.local
```
